525
00:35:35,018 --> 00:35:39,320
Mayor Burke has planned economic meetings to assess where we are and where we need to be

526
00:35:39,868 --> 00:35:44,511
for Medford's commercial success, satisfying the residents in the area.

527
00:35:44,831 --> 00:35:46,072
I totally support this.

528
00:35:46,152 --> 00:35:48,153
It's the best way to proceed.

